- Added selector-level regression tests for both feature-key and triple extraction in [`test_frame_bm25_selector.py` ](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-5scope-1h-20260518T191418Z-codex-frame_logic/worktrees/agent-codex-frame_logic-packet-000079-20260518_194139/tests/unit/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/test_frame_bm25_selector.py:1350).
